STATE of North Carolina
v.
Eddie Levord TAYLOR No. 132P17 Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 24, 2017 Eddie Levord Taylor, for Taylor, Eddie Levord. Tracy Nayer, Assistant Attorney General, R. Andrew Murray, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 24th of April 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Mecklenburg County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 24th of April 2017."
